\section*{CHEST COMPRESSIONS}
- Place the heel of one hand in the centre of the chest
![](https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2025_06_15_405979558bdd7acc4b59g-24.jpg?height=1120&width=933&top_left_y=550&top_left_x=0)
