- Interlock fingers
- Compress the chest
- Rate $100 \mathrm{~min}^{-1}$
- Depth $4-5 \mathrm{~cm}$ (1.5 to 2 inch)
- Equal compression : relaxation
- When possible change CPR operator every 2 min

